Parmarth Sadna Charitable Trust is a non-profit organization dedicated to the dual mission of spiritual awakening and selfless service. By blending the practice of Sadna (disciplined spiritual practice) with Seva (humanitarian work), the Trust aims to uplift the underprivileged while fostering inner peace and community harmony.

